    <primary-label ref="footermandev"/>

    Item Viewers gather all Items in the game and displays them in a grid next to your Inventory,
    and provides means to search for Items.
    <p/>
    Left-Clicking on any Item will show how to obtain it. For example, clicking a Diamond Sword will show it's crafting recipe.<br/>
    Right-Clicking on any Item will show Recipes that include the Item.
    <p/>
    Pressing <shortcut>A</shortcut> on any Item will add it to the Favorites list,
    which appears on the left side of the Inventory.<br/>
    Pressing <shortcut>A</shortcut> again will remove it from the Favorites list.
