    <chapter title="Search Features" id="search">
        There are several extra ways to search Items. For example, Prefixes:
        <list>
            <li><shortcut>@</shortcut> Searches by Mod Name</li>
            <li><shortcut>$</shortcut> Searches by Tag name, or OreDict for 1.12.2 and older.</li>
            <li><shortcut>%</shortcut> Searches by Creative Tab. </li>
            <li><shortcut>#</shortcut> Searches for text in Tooltips.</li>
        </list>
        Additionally, typing <shortcut>|</shortcut> between two sets of text will search for both at the same time.
        <p/>
        Example usages:<br/>
        <code>@mekanism</code> Shows all Items from the Mekanism mod.<br/>
        <code>@minecraft ingot</code> Shows all Items from Minecraft that include the word "Ingot".<br/>
        <code>$minecraft:block/banners</code> Shows all Banners from the Banners tag.<br/>
    </chapter>

